pkgmetadata.longdescription: # Pipeline Engines Fiftyone![51Degrees](https://51degrees.com/DesktopModules/FiftyOne/Distributor/Logo.ashx?utm_source=github&utm_medium=repository&utm_content=readme_main&utm_campaign=python-open-source "Data rewards the curious") **Python Pipeline Engines**[Developer Documentation](https://51degrees.com/pipeline-python/index.html?utm_source=github&utm_medium=repository&utm_content=readme_main&utm_campaign=python-open-source "Developer Documentation")## IntroductionThe Pipeline is a generic web request intelligence and data processing solution with the ability to add a range of 51Degrees and/or custom plug ins (Engines) ## This package fiftyone_pipeline_engines_fiftyoneIt includes a ShareUsage engine that sends usage data to 51Degrees in zipped batches.## Requirements * Python 3.8+
